        public void processEntries()

      • generateRawSpreadsheet

        public boolean generateRawSpreadsheet(java.io.File outputDirectory)
        Generates a spreadsheet of all values from scout entries, with one row per entry. Columns are metric names, and cells contain individual values. Also creates a spreadsheet with "no show" entries removed.
        Parameters:
        outputDirectory - Output directory for generated fields
        Returns:
        True if the method was successfully executed, false otherwise

      • generatePicklists

        public void generatePicklists(java.io.File outputDirectory,
                              int[] knownPartners)
        Creates a compare points list, a pick points list, and a predicted point contribution list for the teams at the current event
        Parameters:
        outputDirectory - Directory where the picklists are saved to
        knownPartners - Array of team numbers that are already in the playoff alliance

      • generateMatchPredictions

        public boolean generateMatchPredictions(java.io.File outputDirectory)
        Creates a text file of future predicted match scores and ranking points, the teams playing on each alliance in the match, the predicted winner of the match, and the confidence in that prediction. Match schedule must be downloaded for this method to work.
        Parameters:
        outputDirectory - Directory to save the prediction text file
        Returns:
        True if the file was created successfully, false otherwise
